OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FA former prison guard was shot dead in
OL,7,F"an act of retaliation" after he
OL,8,Fexposed an illicit relationship
OL,9,Fbetween a convict and a female
OL,10,Fofficer, a jury has heard.
OL,12,FLenny Scott, 33, was fatally injured
OL,13,Fwhen he was shot outside a gym on Peel
OL,14,FRoad in Skelmersdale on February 8th
OL,15,Flast year, by a gunman dressed in a hi-
OL,16,Fvis jacket.
OL,18,FTwo men, Elias Morgan and Anthony
OL,19,FCleary, have gone on trial at Preston
OL,20,FCrown Court accused of the murder of
OL,21,FMr Scott.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
