OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FAlex Leach KC told the court that Mr
OL,7,FScott was working as a prison officer
OL,8,Fat HMP Altcourse when he searched
OL,9,FMorgan's cell and found the phone on
OL,10,FMarch 26th 2020.
OL,12,FThe court heard not only was
OL,13,Fpossession of the phone a criminal
OL,14,Foffence, but "Morgan knew there was
OL,15,Fevidence on it which would lead to the
OL,16,Fdiscovery of a sexual relationship
OL,17,Fbetween him and a female prison
OL,18,Fofficer".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
