OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FMr Leach told the jury that Morgan
OL,7,Ftold Mr Scott to "balls up the
OL,8,Fpaperwork" and even offered #1,500 not
OL,9,Fto report it.
OL,11,FBut the prison officer submitted the
OL,12,Fpaperwork - and from that moment
OL,13,F"Elias Morgan told Lenny Scott that he
OL,14,Fwould get him, he said he would bide
OL,15,Fhis time, but that he would get him".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
