OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FThe prosecutor went on to say: "On the
OL,7,F8th February 2024, almost four years
OL,8,Flater, Lenny Scott was coming out of
OL,9,Fhis gym at Peel House in Skelmersdale
OL,10,Fwhen he was approached by a man
OL,11,Fwearing a high-visibility jacket and
OL,12,Fcarrying a handgun."
OL,14,F"The man shot him, six times, to the
OL,15,Fhead and body. Lenny Scott died of his
OL,16,Finjuries."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
