OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,F"The man travelled to and escaped from
OL,7,Fthe scene on an electric motorbike,
OL,8,Fwhich he loaded onto the back of a
OL,9,Fvan, a short distance away, before
OL,10,Fdriving back towards Liverpool."
OL,12,F"The murder was, the prosecution says,
OL,13,Fan act of retaliation."
OL,15,F"The prosecution says that once you've
OL,16,Fheard the evidence, you will be sure
OL,17,Fthat, at the very least, Elias Morgan
OL,18,Forchestrated Lenny Scott's murder,
OL,19,Frecruiting Anthony Cleary to assist
OL,20,Fhim in doing so.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
