OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,F"That alone would make him guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder on count one."
OL,9,F"Moreover, the prosecution say, when
OL,10,Fyou've examined the fine detail of the
OL,11,Fevidence, you will be sure not only
OL,12,Fthat Elias Morgan is guilty of murder
OL,13,Fby organising the killing of Lenny
OL,14,FScott, you will be sure that it was he
OL,15,Fwho pulled the trigger himself."
OL,17,F"For his part, Anthony Cleary, the
OL,18,Fsecond defendant, played a supporting
OL,19,Frole."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
