OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard in the days after Mr
OL,7,FScott found the phone, he was
OL,8,Fthreatened in three main ways. He told
OL,9,Fhis dad, Neil Scott, who said that
OL,10,F"Lenny had told him that Elias Morgan
OL,11,Fhad said words to the effect of: 'I'll
OL,12,Fbide my time, but I promise I will get
OL,13,Fyou', before making a gun gesture
OL,14,Ftowards him."
