OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FMr Leach said Mr Scott was "visibly
OL,7,Ffrightened" and told his former
OL,8,Fpartner, Lucy Carnill, who was the mum
OL,9,Fof his young daughter, that Morgan had
OL,10,Fthreatened him, that his "home would
OL,11,Fbe blown up with his family inside and
OL,12,Fthat, to reinforce the threat, Elias
OL,13,FMorgan had named his children".
OL,15,FHe also gave similar accounts to his
OL,16,Fmum Paula Scott and his then partner
OL,17,FLucy Griffiths.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
