OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FFour days later Mr Scott, who was also
OL,7,Fthe father of twins, called the police
OL,8,Fand told a call handler "I'm in fear
OL,9,Ffor my family's life".
OL,11,FThe jury heard he also reported the
OL,12,F"threats" to the Prison Service,
OL,13,Falleging that Morgan had asked him
OL,14,F"how much to get that nicking squashed
OL,15,Fand lose the phone?" and that his
OL,16,Ffamily would be hurt if he did not
OL,17,F"drop the nicking".
