OL,6,FThe iPhone was examined and "revealed
OL,7,FElias Morgan was engaged in a sexual
OL,8,Frelationship with another prison
OL,9,Fofficer, Sarah Williams", the court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FMr Leach added: "It was clear that she
OL,13,Fhad provided Elias Morgan with details
OL,14,Fabout other prisoners.
OL,16,FThe court heard Mr Scott gave a
OL,17,Fwitness statement and Morgan was
OL,18,Farrested and interviewed under caution.
