OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FMorgan was remanded back into custody
OL,7,Fbetween July 2021 and October 2022 -
OL,8,Fand in April 2023 was charged with
OL,9,Funauthorised possession of the mobile
OL,10,Fphone Mr Scott had seized.
OL,12,FWilliams admitted three offences of
OL,13,Fmisconduct in a public officer and a
OL,14,Fcomputer misuse offence.
OL,16,FMorgan pleaded not guilty - and his
OL,17,Fcase was adjourned until February 19th
OL,18,F- 11 days after Mr Scott was killed.
