OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard Mr Scott was dismissed
OL,7,Ffrom the Prison Service in April 2021
OL,8,Fafter he punched a prisoner in the
OL,9,Fface in an unrelated incident.
OL,11,FThe court heard Morgan and Cleary were
OL,12,Fpictured together at Glastonbury
OL,13,FFestival in June 2023.
OL,15,FLater the same year, phones used by
OL,16,Fthe two men were both using cell sites
OL,17,Fin southern Spain, the jury heard.
OL,19,FMorgan flew back to Europe on December
OL,20,F23 of that year, before he returned
OL,21,Fback to the UK on January 3rd 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
