OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,FMr Leach said the prosecution's case
OL,7,Fwas on that day Morgan used as a "day
OL,8,Fof reconnaissance", with either his
OL,9,Fcar or phone flagging on systems at
OL,10,Fthree locations linked to Mr Scott -
OL,11,Fthe Mecca Gym in Speke, Mr Scott's
OL,12,Fhome address in Prescot and a gym at
OL,13,FPeel House in Skelmersdale, outside
OL,14,Fwhere he was shot dead in February
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FMr Leach said: "The prosecution say
OL,18,Fthat the combination of locations that
OL,19,FElias Morgan and his associates
OL,20,Fvisited that day is telling."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
