OL,3,CFormer prison guard shot dead in 'act
OL,4,Cof retaliation', court hears
OL,6,F"Taken alone, each of those locations
OL,7,Fhad an obvious connection to Lenny
OL,8,FScott."
OL,10,F"However, taken in combination, Elias
OL,11,FMorgan's visit to Lenny Scott's former
OL,12,Fgym, to the area of Lenny Scott's home
OL,13,Fand then to the location of Lenny
OL,14,FScott's current gym - the location at
OL,15,Fwhich we now know he was to be shot,
OL,16,Fprovides a clear picture, the
OL,17,Fprosecution say, of Elias Morgan using
OL,18,Fthe third of January as a day of
OL,19,Freconnaissance, a day of planning, for
OL,20,Fthe murder that was to follow."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
